Given an integer n, find and print the sum of numbers from 1 to n.
Note : Use while loop only.
Input Format :
Integer n
Output Format :
Sum
Constraints :
1 <= n <= 100
Sample Input :
10
Sample Output :
55
------------------------------------------------------------------SOLUTION-------------------------------------------------------------------


n = int(input())
i = 1
Sum = 0
while i <= n:
    Sum = Sum + i
    i += 1
print(Sum)
